                    <span class="expandToggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="FAQ-content">
                    <p>Resetting your password is like improving water quality for irrigation. Just as you'd adjust the SAR or Na% to maintain ideal conditions, resetting your password helps keep your account "irrigation-ready" and free of any access issues.</p>
