                            <li>Click on the change password button. Hooray! Your password has been successfully updated!</li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="item">
                <div class="FAQ-title">
                    <p class="faqQuestion">4. How do I change my password?</p>
                    <span class="expandToggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="FAQ-content">
                    <p>Changing your password is similar to adjusting the pH levels in irrigation water. It keeps everything in balance and ensures smooth operation. A well-balanced account, like properly managed water, helps avoid disruptions!</p>
                    <p>Steps:
                        <ol>
                            <li>Log into your account and navigate to the <a href="/change_password">Change Password Page</a>.</li>
                            <li>Enter your current password, followed by your new password.</li>
                            <li>Click 'Submit' to update your password and maintain balance.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="item">
                <div class="FAQ-title">
                    <p class="faqQuestion">5. How do I update my account details?</p>
                    <span class="expandToggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="FAQ-content">
                    <p>Updating your account details is like tuning your irrigation map to ensure water flows exactly where it’s needed. By keeping your info up to date, you ensure every drop of account-related information reaches its destination smoothly!</p>
                    <p>Steps:
                        <ol>
                            <li>Log into your account and go to the <a href="/update_profile">Profile Update Page</a>.</li>
                            <li>Edit the necessary fields like email, phone number, or address.</li>
                            <li>Click 'Save' to update your information and keep everything running smoothly.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="item">
                <div class="FAQ-title">
                    <p class="faqQuestion">6. I forgot my password. How can I retrieve it?</p>
                    <span class="expandToggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="FAQ-content">
                    <p>Forgetting your password is like a sudden drought on your irrigation field. Don't worry though, just like refilling your reservoir, you can easily recover access by following the steps to retrieve or reset your password.</p>
                    <p>Steps:
                        <ol>
                            <li>Visit the <a href="/forgot_password">Forgot Password Page</a>.</li>
                            <li>Enter your registered email to receive a password reset link.</li>
                            <li>Follow the link and set a new password to regain access.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="FAQ-ShowMore">
                <button id="showMoreBtn2">Show More</button>
            </div>

        </div>

